	<div class='col-md-12'>
		<h1 class='display-3'>Every idea counts</h1>
		<h2 class='display-5'>Here’s how the process works</h2>
		<div class='card-deck'>
			<div class='card'>
				<div class='card-body'>
				<h5 class='card-title'>
					Your idea starts as a Spark.
				</h5>
				<p class='card-text'>
					Using the Lean Canvas approach (<a href='http://www.leanstack.com'>www.leanstack.com</a>), 
					fill in the initial submission form.  Please be as detailed as possible. For a Spark, you only need to identify the target
					customer segment, the problem description, a solution, and a unique value proposition.
				</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class='card'>
				<div class='card-body'>
				<h5 class='card-title'>
					Your Peers Vote for Ideas.
				</h5>
				<p class='card-text'>
					The list of submitted ideas is available to everyone in the company. 
					Browse through the list to vote other ideas up or down. When you feel 
					you have enough support, identify a launchpad sponsor, 
					and hit "Submit" to bring your idea to the Launchpad.
				</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class='card'>
				<div class='card-body'>
				<h5 class='card-title'>
					Discuss &amp; Debate.
				</h5>
				<p class='card-text'>
					Attend the next Launchpad meeting, to discus and debate the idea.				
				</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class='card'>
				<div class='card-body'>
				<h5 class='card-title'>
					Get Started: Build, Learn, Measure.
				</h5>
				<p class='card-text'>
					If approved to move forward, we will prioritize your suggestion and 
					keep you updated on its progress.
				</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
